---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout description="Our privacy policy explains how we collect and use your information when you purchase resources or request custom commissions." title="Privacy Â· CD">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 sm:py-20 lg:px-8">
    <div class="sm:pb:20 flex flex-col gap-4 pb-16 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-medium tracking-tight sm:text-5xl">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-base">Last update: December 31, 2024</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="mb-4">
        At CiviCraft Development, we value your privacy and are dedicated to protecting the personal
        information you share with us when purchasing Minecraft resources or requesting custom
        commissions. This Privacy Policy explains what data we collect, how we use it, and your
        rights regarding your information. Please read carefully.
      </p>
      <h2 class="mb-6 mt-12 text-xl font-medium sm:text-2xl">1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        We collect the following types of personal information to provide and improve our services:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-inside list-disc space-y-4">
        <li>
          Order details: When you purchase a resource or request a commission, we may collect
          your name, email address, payment information, and any additional details related to your
          order.
        </li>
        <li>
          Communication information: If you contact us, we may collect details from your
          correspondence to address your queries or concerns.
        </li>
        <li>
          Usage data: We may collect data about how you use our website, such as your IP
          address, browser type, and browsing behavior, to improve the experience.
        </li>
        <li>
          Cookies: We use cookies to enhance your experience, track order history, and manage
          your preferences.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <h2 class="mb-6 mt-12 text-xl font-medium sm:text-2xl">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        Your information is used to ensure smooth operations and enhance your experience:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-inside list-disc space-y-4">
        <li>
          Order fulfillment: To process payments, complete commissions, and deliver purchased
          resources.
        </li>
        <li>
          Customer support: To respond to your inquiries and provide support for your orders or
          commissions.
        </li>
        <li>
          Improvement: To understand how users interact with our services and improve our
          offerings.
        </li>
        <li>
          Marketing: With your consent, we may send updates on new resources, promotions, or
          commission openings. You can opt-out at any time.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <h2 class="mb-6 mt-12 text-xl font-medium sm:text-2xl">3. Your Rights</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal information. To exercise
        these rights, please contact us using the details below.
      </p>
      <h2 class="mb-6 mt-12 text-xl font-medium sm:text-2xl">Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or how your information is handled,
        please contact us at <b>privacy@civicraft.net</b>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
